    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s an absolute gem that\u2019s been garage-kept and totally babied since day one. Honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for something in truly pristine condition that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel\u2014come check it out!",
