      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car, and honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape\u2014sparkling clean inside and out, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! I'm sad to let it go, but I'm sure the next owner will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
