      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously maintained E46 M3, representing a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 inline-six engine remains in peak mechanical health, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been structurally reinforced at the subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventive measure\u2014and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings. This example exhibits zero fluid seepage and features a pristine undercarriage, retaining its original torsional rigidity and high-revving throttle response. A true driver\u2019s specimen with no deferred maintenance.",
